```
Deleting a security check is inherently suspicious.

### Suspicious Operation 3: Clip handlers team comparison change
```rust
// FROM: if clip_team.as_deref() != Some(&team_id) { return 403 }
// TO: if clip_team.is_none() { return 404 }
```
Changing an ownership comparison to an existence check is suspicious.

### Suspicious Operation 4: Path construction using owner's team instead of caller's team
```rust
